### Norscode Helpdesk API (smoke)

### 1) Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/health

### 2) List all tickets
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: user

### 2b) List assigned to Lena (latest first)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?assignee=lena&sort=-created_at
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2c) List by creator
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?created_by=anna
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2d) List by created_at asc
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?sort=created_at
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: user

### 2e) List by created_at desc
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?sort=-created_at
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: user

### 2f) List by updated_at asc
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?sort=updated_at
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: user

### 2g) List by updated_at desc
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?sort=-updated_at
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: user

### 2h) My tickets (assigned to me)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?filter=assigned
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: lena

### 2i) My tickets (unassigned)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?filter=unassigned
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: lena

### 2j) My tickets sorted by updated_at desc
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?sort=-updated_at
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2k) My tickets paged
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?sort=-updated_at&limit=5&offset=0
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2m) Invalid sort should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?sort=bad-sort
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2p) Invalid tickets status should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?status=bad
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2q) Invalid short search query should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?q=a
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2r) Invalid empty assignee filter should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?assignee=
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2s) Invalid empty created_by filter should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?created_by=
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2n) Invalid my-filter should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?filter=bad
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2o) Invalid my-status should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?status=bad
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2u) Invalid tickets limit should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?limit=0
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2v) Invalid tickets offset should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?offset=-1
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2v2) Invalid tickets limit should return error (too high)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?limit=201
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2v3) Invalid tickets offset should return error (too high)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?offset=10001
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2v4) Invalid tickets limit should return error (not a number)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets?limit=abc
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent

### 2w) Invalid my-sort should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?sort=bad
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2x) Invalid my-limit should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?limit=-1
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2y) Invalid my-offset should return error
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?offset=abc
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2z) Invalid my-limit should return error (too high)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?limit=201
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2aa) Invalid my-offset should return error (too high)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?offset=10001
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 2l) My open tickets
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/tickets/my?status=open
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
x-Role: agent
x-user: anna

### 3a) Admin users list
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/users
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin

### 3b) Admin roles list
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/roles
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin

### 3c) Admin set user role
POST http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/users
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin
x-user: admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": "konsulent",
  "role": "agent"
}

### 3d) Admin override ticket update
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/tickets/1
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin
x-user: admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "open",
  "assignee": "anna"
}

### 3e) Admin hard delete ticket
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/tickets/9999
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin
x-user: admin

### 3f) Admin audit log (paged)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/audit?limit=10&offset=0
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin

### 3g) Non-admin cannot access admin users
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/users
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: user

### 3h) Admin metrics
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/metrics
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
X-Role: admin

### 3j) Admin panel (HTML)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4173/admin/panel
X-API-Key: secret-helpdesk
